        "subject": "LU-16925 osd-ldiskfs: Make CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY optional",
        "message": "LU-16925 osd-ldiskfs: Make CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY optional\n\nWhen CONFIG_BLK_DEV_INTEGRITY is not enabled struct blk_integrity\nmake not be defined along with the enum values for\nBLK_INTEGRITY_VERIFY and BLK_INTEGRITY_GENERATE,\n\nLustre will provide a bio_integrity_enabled() however the function\nshould just return false.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-10118\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ie4b1fb13204f8e3cf3738c7c21584fa919513a5b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
